        <div class='row main'>
          <div class='col-md-6'>
            <h2>删除帐户<br><small>将您的帐户彻底地从系统中删除。</small></h2>
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-6 module_delAccount'>
            <button class='btn btn-danger btn-lg' v-on:click="delaccountOps()">删除我的帐户</button>
